    "description": "UC6 Step 8: Reconciliation cash-in-transit for Master FBO side. Reclassifies customer allocation balances through Cash in Transit on the allocation ledger. Leg 1 moves between Cash Balances Clearing (11901) and Cash Balances Suspense (11903). Leg 2 moves between Customer Master FBO (21100) and Customer Cash in Transit (21801). Direction depends on whether the customer's sweep is inbound or outbound.",
